title: What Does 'Justice League' Have in Common With Radiohead’s 'OK Computer'? (Ep. 136)
description:
The Ringer’s Chris Ryan and Andy Greenwald discuss the new trailer for DC’s 'Justice League' (2:00) before revisiting the cultural significance of Radiohead’s 'OK Computer' 20 years after its release (13:16). Then Andy recommends a new TV show (42:40).
